parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or slip out of gear, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Transmission slipping
hesitation
or failure to engage gears
especially in second gear; sudden loss of power; vehicle stalling; harsh gear shifting noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission interlock can cause the vehicle to roll away, even when the driver thinks it is in park, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Key can be removed from the ignition with the transmission in neutral; vehicle rolls away even when shifted into park; difficulty shifting into park.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch hydraulic system can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Clutch pedal feels soft or spongy; clutch pedal sticks to the floor; clutch pedal does not return to its normal position; clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of Takata airbag recall parts can lead to delayed or incomplete repairs, leaving vehicles with potentially defective airbags that can cause injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Notification of recall
but parts are not available
dealerships unable to repair
and lack of communication from manufacturer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a malfunction in the airbag system, which can lead to airbag failure or unintended deployment, causing injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Airbag warning light remains illuminated
airbag light flashes intermittently
and airbag malfunction warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended airbag deployment or failure to deploy can cause injuries or fatalities, and can also lead to accidents or loss of vehicle control.
symptoms: Airbag deployed without cause
airbag did not deploy in an accident
and airbag malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the auto-dimming rearview mirror can cause a corrosive fluid to leak onto the interior of the vehicle, damaging the console, seats, and carpet. The fluid can also be toxic and cause health problems if inhaled.
symptoms: The rearview mirror becomes distorted or cloudy
a clear bubble appears at the top of the mirror glass
the mirror leaks a dark fluid
the fluid corrodes the console and other interior components
and a strong chemical smell is present in the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The windshield wiper can leave a black film on the windshield, impairing the driver's vision.
symptoms: The windshield wiper leaves a black film or slanted imprint on the windshield
impairing the driver's vision.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The side view mirror can create a large blind spot, particularly on the right side, resulting in poor visibility.
symptoms: The side view mirror creates a large blind spot
making it difficult to see other vehicles or pedestrians when making turns.
